# Splunk Scheduling Reports & Alerts Lab

## 📌 Overview
This project documents my hands-on practice with **Splunk Scheduling Reports & Alerts**, completed as part of my Splunk Core Certified User training. It demonstrates how to automate searches, configure alerts, and manage notifications in a SIEM environment.

---

## 🔑 Skills Practiced
- Creating and scheduling reports
- Configuring real-time and interval alerts
- Setting throttling rules to limit alert noise
- Managing permissions for reports and alerts
- Testing trigger conditions and reviewing triggered actions

---

## 📂 Contents
- `queries/` → SPL queries used in the lab
- `screenshots/` → Key steps and results (reports, alerts firing)
- `video/` → Recorded walkthrough of the lab (optional link or upload)
- `README.md` → Documentation of steps and lessons learned

